{
  "stem": "3341.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How to save this poor woman?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What shall we do with her?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she was able to, to hide her with one of the employees from the shop, which she was very good.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A poor woman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe she gave her money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was hiding there for one night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then she had to find the other place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was carrying her how?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the evening from one place to the other till it was possible to, to save her life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When it was very, very hard, because it became harder and harder, she arranged in her own initiative that my mother was taken to the country.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the best part of it is, with the help of the other trustee.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The women who was complete strangers to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But these two women, while they were in the shop, and they were-- that was already more than two years, two and a half years almost That was in '42, beginning of '43, actually.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This woman became more and more friendly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't know that, only after the war we found out, that Mimi-- that is the trustee woman of ours-- she said she couldn't bear it on her own.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she disclosed this one day, especially when she found my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She said, what will I do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she asked the other woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, look.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are from the country because they were country people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What can we do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she arranged, with the other woman, that my mother was secretly taken to the country town and was like a housekeeper with the parents of this second trustee woman which we had.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was a very nice gesture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But don't forget, that was already in '44.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was beginning of '44.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
